### ============================================
### 4.6 RANKING ENDPOINT
### ============================================

### GET /v1/ranking - All time
### Obtener ranking global (todos los usuarios)
GET {{baseUrl}}/ranking?period=all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================

### GET /v1/ranking - Daily
### Obtener ranking diario
GET {{baseUrl}}/ranking?period=daily
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================

### GET /v1/ranking - Weekly
### Obtener ranking semanal
GET {{baseUrl}}/ranking?period=weekly
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================

### GET /v1/ranking - By group
### Obtener ranking por grupo específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/ranking?groupId={{groupId}}&period=daily
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### ERROR CASES
### ============================================

### GET /v1/ranking - Invalid period
GET {{baseUrl}}/ranking?period=invalid
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================

### GET /v1/ranking - Non-existent group
GET {{baseUrl}}/ranking?groupId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================

### GET /v1/ranking - Without auth
GET {{baseUrl}}/ranking?period=all

### ============================================
